{
  "description": "A serene coastal scene unfolds with golden sand meeting the turquoise waves of the ocean. Gentle waves roll towards the shore, creating a frothy white edge as they break. The beach, covered in fine sand and scattered with small pebbles, stretches into the distance, gently curving to the left. In the background, distant cliffs and landforms are visible, partially obscured by a soft haze. Above, a bright blue sky is adorned with wispy, white clouds. The overall impression is one of peacefulness and natural beauty.",
